librknnrt.so - Rockchip RKNN Neural Network Runtime Library
============================================================

Source:
  https://github.com/airockchip/rknpu2/raw/master/runtime/RK356X/Linux/librknn_api/aarch64/librknnrt.so

Purpose:
  Provides NPU (Neural Processing Unit) inference support for Rockchip RK356X/RK3588
  series SoCs. Enables AI model inference acceleration using the on-chip NPU hardware.

Install path:
  /usr/local/lib/librknnrt.so

Usage:
  Run `ldconfig` after placing the file to update the dynamic linker cache.
  Verify with: `ldconfig -p | grep librknnrt`

